OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FThe current system is bound by the
OL,7,F1975 Social Security Overlapping of
OL,8,FBenefits order, which dictates
OL,9,Fislanders can only claim one benefit
OL,10,Fat a time - so either their pension or
OL,11,Fthe Home Carers' Allowance (HCA).
OL,13,FThe review found allowing islanders to
OL,14,Fclaim both benefits could cost the
OL,15,Fgovernment up to #7.5 million more
OL,16,Feach year - with an estimated 500
OL,17,Fpensioner carers on-island who would
OL,18,Fthen be eligible to make dual claims.
