OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FWith the island's ageing population,
OL,7,Fthe department's modelling predicts
OL,8,Fthis cost burden would only increase
OL,9,Fin years to come, and would require
OL,10,Fnew funding streams - potentially
OL,11,Fforcing the department to increase
OL,12,Fislanders' social security
OL,13,Fcontributions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
