OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FThey add allowing individuals to claim
OL,7,Fboth HCA and their pension would be of
OL,8,Fno benefit to carers of working age,
OL,9,F"who may be struggling more
OL,10,Ffinancially" - and argue it would
OL,11,Fencourage these working carers to
OL,12,Fstarting claiming multiple benefits
OL,13,Falongside the HCA, too.
OL,15,FHowever, their decision leaves
OL,16,Fislanders like Mark - who cares full-
OL,17,Ftime for his two children - unable to
OL,18,Fclaim any of the pension he's paid
OL,19,Finto his whole life.
