OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FPeople claiming HCA are able to also
OL,7,Fhave paid employment for a maximum of
OL,8,F15 hours a week, and the 69-year-old
OL,9,Ffather worked at the same accountancy
OL,10,Fpractice for 32 years.
OL,12,F"My employer was paying six and half
OL,13,Fpercent of my salary and I was paying
OL,14,Fin six - so there was what I would say
OL,15,Fwas quite a lot in my pot", he
OL,16,Fexplains.
OL,18,F"So when I found out I wasn't entitled
OL,19,Fto it I thought it just can't be
OL,20,Fright."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
