OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F382A1769900574
OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FThe most he can do is 'top-up' his
OL,7,Fpension so that it equates to the full
OL,8,Fvalue of HCA.
OL,10,FThe report concludes that "the
OL,11,Fsuggested change would not address the
OL,12,Fmain concerns raised by carers, would
OL,13,Fnot be targeted at people who need the
OL,14,Fmost financial support, and would come
OL,15,Fat considerable cost.
OL,17,F"Therefore the Minister has no plans
OL,18,Fto make any changes to the current
OL,19,Frules in respect of overlapping
OL,20,Fcontributory benefits".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
