OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FGuernsey changed their benefits laws
OL,7,Fto allow people to claim both their
OL,8,Fpension and HCA in 2018.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News in response to
OL,11,Fthe review's publication, Mark says he
OL,12,Fwould have liked to clarify the point
OL,13,Fin the minister statement that said
OL,14,F"carers did not consider the overlap
OL,15,Fof benefits a priority."
OL,17,FHe said: "I would question how may of
OL,18,Fthe carers interviewed were in a
OL,19,Fsimilar position to mine?"
