OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,FHe adds that whilst he is "obviously
OL,7,Fdisappointed that the review has not
OL,8,Fresulted in the outcome I and others
OL,9,Fwanted", he is still "very pleased"
OL,10,Fthat the review took place and "there
OL,11,Fwill (now) be more support for carers
OL,12,Fin general.
OL,14,F"The campaign has been worth it in
OL,15,Fthat respect - (but) I do wonder why
OL,16,Fit took my campaign before the States
OL,17,Fdeemed a review necessary."
OL,19,FThe review resulted in several major
OL,20,Fchanges to other elements of the
OL,21,Fbenefits system, including:
