OL,3,C'More work to be done' to support
OL,4,Cunpaid carers in Jersey
OL,6,F"We also support the initiatives with
OL,7,Fregard to funding, including the
OL,8,Fexplanation of Home Carer's Allowance
OL,9,Fand pension payments", they continue.
OL,11,F"However, we recognise there is still
OL,12,Fmore work to be undertaken in this
OL,13,Fimportant area."
OL,15,FDeputy Feltham says she remains
OL,16,F"committed to working closely with
OL,17,Fcarers' organisations and, most
OL,18,Fimportantly, listening to carers
OL,19,Fthemselves" in her work going forwards.
